		<b>Comment By Hal Herring, 4-16-06</b>
		<p>Jenny,<br />
<br />
What a cool thing to find on this site. I was fascinated by the nuts and bolts of storytelling outlined in this piece. I'd like to take a class taught by David Jacobs or Haarhoff, or any of these folks. Cindy Bonner nailed why I, too, left Syriana feeling like the movie had made a fantastic shot at something, had everything, was important, but still just did not work. <br />
I really like what you've done here.<br />
<br />
Hal Herring</p>
		
